      <text id="frontgrille" xmlEditRichText="false">NEW GRILLE</text>
      <text id="frontgrille_pa" xmlEditRichText="false">A more elegant grille, enlarged Iron Mark and larger air intake emphasises the new C70’s more confident stance.</text>
      <text id="headlights" xmlEditRichText="false">NEW HEADLAMPS</text>
      <text id="headlights_pa" xmlEditRichText="false">The new angled headlamps are elegantly swept back to dramatically enhance the new C70’s sophisticated good looks.</text>
      <text id="foglamps" xmlEditRichText="false">NEW FOGLAMPS</text>
      <text id="foglamps_pa" xmlEditRichText="false">The modernised foglamp décore reveals traces of the S60 Concept Car, while blending seamlessly with the car’s natural elegance.</text>
      <text id="retractable_roof" xmlEditRichText="false">3-PART ROOF</text>
      <text id="retractable_roof_pa" xmlEditRichText="false">The retractable 3-part roof smoothly transforms an elegant coupe into a sporty convertible in less than 30 seconds.</text>
      <text id="body_color" xmlEditRichText="false">NEW COLOUR</text>
      <text id="body_color_pa" xmlEditRichText="false">The new C70’s dramatic new lines are further enhanced by a seductive new colour: Flamenco Red Metallic.</text>
      <text id="rear_taillights" xmlEditRichText="false">NEW REAR LIGHTS</text>
      <text id="rear_taillights_pa" xmlEditRichText="false">Exclusive high-tech LED lamps elegantly blend into the oval framing the new C70’s rear panel.</text>
